Class IntervalGeneratorUniform

  • java.lang.Object
    • IntervalGenerator
      • IntervalGeneratorUniform

  • class IntervalGeneratorUniform
extends IntervalGenerator
    The class generates values according to uniform distribution with parameters a and b. a and b are the smallest and the highest possible value. In our context, the values means time intervals between consecutive packet generations.
